	     <tr><td id="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top"><a id="sj" href="/db/item.html?item=16420&amp;mid=105093983485264">RE: So...</a> <a id="fs8" href="/db/item.html?item=16420&amp;mid=105093983485264#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." width="17" height="11" /></a>
	     <br clear="all" /><small>Posted @ Mon, Apr 21st 12:22 PM 2003</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=111670"><span id="Sage">Vorish</span></a><br /><b><span id="Sage">Sage</span></b><br /><span id="notbold">308 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score:</span> Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Requires a toolbox (8 or 10 slot), Mana Battery - Class Six (storebought or looted).&nbsp;&nbsp;To recharge, put the two items in the toolbox and click combine.  Requires no skill and does not require that you be a gnome.<br/><br/>Sold by Maryalis N'Ryt at neg 850 pos 200 in PoK (evil/south side of PoK, easternmost building between the Neriak and Ogguk portal stones, inside through the door on the left).  <br/><br/>Price was 106pp with 100 CHA.  This means that the per-use cost is only ~5pp vs ~15pp for a shrink potion.  I paid 700pp for my device, which means that after only 70 uses, I'll have paid it off.<br/><br/>(As mentioned in this thread: <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=16414&amp;mid=104361072612178" target=_new>http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=16414&amp;mid=104361072612178</a>)<br/><br/>All tinkered items can be recharged in this manner (different items require different batteries).<br/><br/><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Apr 21 11:50:09 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
